# Studio Manager Beta Must...

Use this article to track features and capabilities the absolutely have to be viable for March release.
##The MUST Things
 
* Manage and track Limited Editions (including quantity=1)
    * I'm on the fence regarding Use Editions
* Manage and track Open Editions
* Create and manage Groups and their Members
* Must be responsive
    * Does it have to be fully mobile-ready?
    * Is there a reason to be responsive other than to be mobile-usable given that goolgle will not index these pages and so there is no responsive requirement?


## The OPTIONAL Things

* Implement Series
* Implement Subscription
